    {
        "content": "<p>I'm not sure if this is the best method, but didn't wan to start new thread not directly connected with rust in linux but development environment.<br>\nI run my qemu with rusted-kernel inside VM virtualbox ubuntu. Internet works there. I run machine with:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">qemu</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">system</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">x86_64</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">nographic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">vmlinux</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">initrd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">../</span><span class=\"n\">busybox</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ramdisk</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">img</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">nic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">model</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">rtl8139</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">hostfwd</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">tcp</span>::<span class=\"mi\">5555</span><span class=\"o\">-</span>:<span class=\"mi\">23</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">hostfwd</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">tcp</span>::<span class=\"mi\">5556</span><span class=\"o\">-</span>:<span class=\"mi\">8080</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>eth0 is up and with ip form dhcp client like Wedson shown in yt environment setup<br>\nfrom busybox I cannot ping google dns 8.8.8.8 - addres not recognized<br>\nwhen I connect from outside to 5555 the header from telnet show up but no prompt served with sh<br>\nwhen I connect to 127.0.0.1 port 23 with client telnet works inside machine<br>\non 5556, compiled-in rust echo server is dumb, no response, but when I connect inside the qemu machine it repeat with correct echo</p>\n<p>What can be wrong, what can be missing?</p>",
        "id": 367642669,
        "sender_full_name": "Adam Mierzwiak",
        "timestamp": 1687181608
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>in /etc/init.d/rcS i have this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">mkdir</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">proc</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">proc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">none</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">proc</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">ifconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">up</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ifconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">eth0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">up</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">udhcpc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">eth0</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devtmpfs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">none</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mkdir</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">pts</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devpts</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">nodev</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">pts</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">telnetd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">l</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\" File $0 processed succesfully\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
