        "content": "<p>Qemu doesn't support icmp (ping) for the userspace network implementation. Tcp and udp should work fine. If you really need icmp to work you will have to setup a tun/tap device and tell qemu to use it which requires root and last time I tried didn't manage to get working.</p>",
        "id": 367767350,
        "sender_full_name": "bjorn3",
